<div id="txtcont" class="span9" style="position: relative;">
    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='155:181'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-1a' );" name="014-1a" class="pb">[014-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='181:189'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='189:198'>　詩總聞卷十四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='198:218'>　　　　　　　　　　　　宋　王質　撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='218:224'>　　甫田</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='224:231'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='231:241'>倬彼甫田嵗取十千</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='241:264'>　孔氏凡詩之作非如記事之書必詳度量之數甫田</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='264:287'>　言嵗取十千亦猶頌之萬億及秭舉成數耳計其所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='287:313'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-1b' );" name="014-1b" class="pb">[014-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='313:336'>　在大田皆有十千之數以見天下皆豐此説甚通他</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='336:342'>　皆倣此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='342:356'>我取其陳食我農人自古有年</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='356:379'>　以舊儲者食以新收者積新陳相因自古遇豐年其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='379:392'>　法如此漢常平之制略似</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='392:414'>今適南畆或耘或耔黍稷薿薿攸介攸止烝我髦士</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='414:437'>　田野亦有髦俊于種藝之間有餘力則助人無餘力</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='437:452'>　則止所可審察其人之賢否也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='452:478'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-2a' );" name="014-2a" class="pb">[014-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='478:485'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='485:499'>以我齊明與我犧羊以社以方</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='499:522'>　齊整也明潔也言穀之精也唯為社事單出里唯為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='522:545'>　社田國人畢作唯社丘乗共粢盛此為社所共者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='545:568'>我田既臧農夫之慶琴瑟擊鼓以御田祖以祈甘雨以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='568:579'>介我稷黍以穀我士女</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='579:602'>　田祖鄭氏先嗇神農司嗇后稷凡國祈年于田祖吹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='602:625'>　豳雅擊土鼓以樂田畯田畯恐亦是田神若是田官</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='625:651'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-2b' );" name="014-2b" class="pb">[014-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='651:661'>　不當與大神同饗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='661:668'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='668:691'>曽孫來止以其婦子饁彼南畆田畯至喜攘其左右嘗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='691:696'>其㫖否</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='696:719'>　七月略同辭至喜不必改為饎言迎其神既至而喜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='719:742'>　也君勞田見之却其左右而嘗其美否與下通懐如</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='742:765'>　此也古禮凡祭神皆有尸今所在尚有此風然多流</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='765:772'>　于邪怪也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='772:798'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-3a' );" name="014-3a" class="pb">[014-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='798:816'>禾易長畆終善且有曽孫不怒農夫克敏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='816:839'>　禾所以易長者以人之克敏也人道敏政地道敏樹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='839:859'>　凡稼事以敏為功所謂痔乃錢鎛奄觀銍艾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='859:866'>　　　四章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='866:889'>曽孫之稼如茨如梁曽孫之庾如坻如京乃求千斯倉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='889:912'>乃求萬斯箱黍稷稻粱農夫之慶報以介福萬壽無疆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='912:935'>　茨布地而生蒺藜也梁截水而横略彴也坻從水而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='935:958'>　起洲渚也京附地而隆陂陁也積穀之状如此倉貯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='958:984'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-3b' );" name="014-3b" class="pb">[014-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='984:1002'>　之本壌者也箱運之以補助他所者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1002:1025'>　　聞音曰畆滿罪切耔奨禮切薿魚起切士鉏里切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1025:1048'>　　　明謨郎切慶墟羊切右羽軌切否補美切有羽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1048:1067'>　　　軌切敏母鄙切京居良切慶墟羊切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1067:1090'>總聞曰前兩詩不知何以見思古此詩又不知何以見</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1090:1113'>思古而傷今當是以自昔何為自古有年遂以為思古</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1113:1136'>以今適南畆遂以為傷今詩援古及今甚多且以田事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1136:1159'>言之振古如兹續古之人皆及古以迄于今匪今斯今</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1159:1185'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-4a' );" name="014-4a" class="pb">[014-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1185:1208'>皆及今雖未敢即以為某王之盛時亦未敢即以為某</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1208:1218'>王之亂世識者更詳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1218:1224'>　　大田</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1224:1231'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1231:1254'>大田多稼既種既戒既備乃事以我覃耜俶載南畆播</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1254:1267'>厥百穀既庭且碩曾孫是若</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1267:1290'>　周制季冬令告民出五種命農既耦耕事修耒耜具</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1290:1313'>　田器所謂既備也孟春命布農事命田舍東郊善相</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1313:1339'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-4b' );" name="014-4b" class="pb">[014-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1339:1362'>　丘陵阪險原隰土地所冝五穀所殖所謂俶載也孟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1362:1385'>　夏命野虞出行田原為天子勸農勞民毋或失時所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1385:1408'>　謂是若也孟夏驅獸毋害五穀季夏燒薙行水利以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1408:1429'>　殺草可糞田疇可美土疆所謂無害也見下章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1429:1436'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1436:1459'>既方既皁既堅既好不稂不莠去其螟螣及其蟊賊無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1459:1473'>害我田穉田祖有神秉畀炎火</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1473:1496'>　稂莠人力所及螟螣蟊賊人力所不及神其以害田</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1496:1522'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-5a' );" name="014-5a" class="pb">[014-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1522:1535'>　之物而畀之火禱之辭也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1535:1542'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1542:1560'>有渰萋萋興雨祁祁雨我公田遂及我私</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1560:1583'>　雨我公田遂及我私民愛君也駿發爾私亦服爾耕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1583:1606'>　君愛民也民愛君以公為先君愛民以私為先耕謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1606:1629'>　公田也雨澤耑及公田因急私田急于公緩于私之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1629:1652'>　辭私則駿發耕則亦服急于私而緩于公之辭當時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1652:1662'>　　君民之情可見</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1662:1688'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-5b' );" name="014-5b" class="pb">[014-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1688:1711'>彼有不穫穉此有不斂穧彼有遺秉此有滯穗伊寡婦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1711:1715'>之利</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1715:1738'>　不穫不及穫者也不斂不及斂者也遺秉所棄者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='1738:1761'>　滯穗所留者也今北方刈穫弱婦幼童隨羣掇拾于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='1761:1780'>　後亦足度日南方亦謂之拾䈉但不多耳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='1780:1787'>　　　四章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='1787:1810'>曽孫來止以其婦子饁彼南畆田畯至喜來方禋祀以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='1810:1827'>其騂黑與其黍稷以享以祀以介景福</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='1827:1853'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-6a' );" name="014-6a" class="pb">[014-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='1853:1876'>　此蜡祭也大率此詩言收成之事為多似是索饗凡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='1876:1899'>　田祭田祖居先田畯次之至此曽孫方來者觀蜡祭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='1899:1906'>　同民福也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='1906:1929'>　　聞音曰稼讀作介今南人猶作此音叶戒事上止</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='1929:1952'>　　　切耜飬里切畆滿罪切穀訖岳切碩常約切皁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='1952:1975'>　　　此苟切好許厚切螣徒得切火虎隈切祀逸織</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='1975:1985'>　　　切福筆力切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='1985:2008'>　　聞訓曰穉説文幼禾也既刈有續生者今謂之稻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2008:2034'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-6b' );" name="014-6b" class="pb">[014-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2034:2057'>　　　孫穧説文撮也秉説文禾束也穗説文禾成秀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2057:2080'>　　　也民間今猶有穧音一截兩截謂之一穧兩穧</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2080:2102'>　　　與穧同亦有穗音一枝兩枝謂之一穗兩穗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2102:2125'>　　聞物曰爾雅食心曰螟食葉曰螣食根曰蟊食節</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2125:2148'>　　　曰賊説文蝗食禾節從虫説是説文又云螣蝗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2148:2171'>　　　也亦以賊為蝗如此則兩句再舉蝗也今田間</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2171:2194'>　　　一種結網罣禾實者從㝠恐是此意今俗謂螟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2194:2217'>　　　虫一種口截禾莖者從矛戈恐是此意今俗謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2217:2243'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-7a' );" name="014-7a" class="pb">[014-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2243:2267'>　　　蝗虫後股如鋸甚利二種皆不食禾而傷禾大率</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2267:2291'>　　　漢儒之學兩物則分作兩種用四物則分作四種</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2291:2315'>　　　用假如虫類更增而物狀不可增則將如何古今</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2315:2340'>　　　遼逺虫之名實亦不可盡合今但多云蝗虫又曰蛉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2340:2362'>　　　虫恐即是螟也其餘會粹之名多與古不侔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2362:2386'>　　聞跡曰詩多稱南畆説見信南山後人言東臯猶可</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2386:2409'>　　　西疇逺失古意或謂多作西成然所謂農人告</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2409:2432'>　　　予以春及將有事于西疇正是春時非是秋時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2432:2458'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-7b' );" name="014-7b" class="pb">[014-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2458:2481'>　　　或植杖而耘耔登東臯而舒嘯正是夏時非是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2481:2504'>　　　春時大率後人乗意指東西南北為辭詩人亦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2504:2524'>　　　率意但所見止在南所謂南東其畝也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2524:2547'>總聞曰八蜡八方之神也各隨其所来之方祀之舉此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2547:2570'>禮耑用豳詩八章當分歌以樂八神鄭氏以為一先嗇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2570:2593'>二司嗇三農四郵表畷五貓虎六坊七水庸八昆蟲恐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2593:2616'>未必然止祝辭可見土歸于宅土神一也宅神二也宅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='2616:2639'>山之間也水歸于壑水神三也壑神四也壑巖穴之間</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='2639:2665'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-8a' );" name="014-8a" class="pb">[014-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='2665:2688'>也昆蟲毋作昆蟲神五也草木歸其澤草神六也木神</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='2688:2711'>七也澤神八也澤陂湖之間也昆當作蜫蟲之總名也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='2711:2735'>既蜡收民息已故既蜡君子不興功蓋神人各來其所也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='2735:2743'>　　瞻彼洛矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='2743:2750'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='2750:2760'>瞻彼洛矣維水泱泱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='2760:2783'>　此必宣王會諸侯東都之時也君子斥宣王也古之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='2783:2800'>　明王莫如文武成康是時亦未宅洛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='2800:2826'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-8b' );" name="014-8b" class="pb">[014-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='2826:2844'>君子至止福禄如茨韎韐有奭以作六師</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='2844:2867'>　至洛會諸侯行大賚有賜之以韎韐之盛而在外統</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='2867:2890'>　師者如方叔之徒是也有賜之以韠之琫珌而内守</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='2890:2902'>　國者如張仲之徒是也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='2902:2909'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='2909:2932'>瞻彼洛矣維水泱泱君子至止韠琫有珌君子萬年保</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='2932:2937'>其家室</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='2937:2944'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='2944:2970'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-9a' );" name="014-9a" class="pb">[014-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='2970:2993'>瞻彼洛矣維水泱泱君子至止福禄既同君子萬年保</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='2993:2998'>其家邦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='2998:3021'>　一章言以作六師兩章皆言保其家室保其家邦人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='3021:3040'>　情不欲多征唯欲内保故皆以萬年祝之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='3040:3055'>　　聞音曰茨前西切邦卜功切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='3055:3078'>　　聞用曰韎韐毛氏茅蒐草也鄭氏從之又茅蒐韎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='3078:3103'>　　　韐聲也毛氏又所以代韠也鄭氏從之言祭服之韠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='3103:3127'>　　　也孔氏韎草名陳留人謂之蒨韎又從毛鄭也又</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='3127:3153'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-9b' );" name="014-9b" class="pb">[014-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='3153:3178'>　　　韎韐以代韠其體合韋之蔽膝之衣是韐又從毛鄭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='3178:3202'>　　　也奭者用茅蒐之草染之故赤孔氏集毛鄭之説</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='3202:3225'>　　　頗明韎集韻音昧音末皆韋赤色韐集韻士服</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='3225:3248'>　　　如韍則韎韐殆類赤韍也禮韎師掌教韎樂鄭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='3248:3271'>　　　氏讀如味飲食之味杜氏讀韎為菋荎著之菋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='3271:3294'>　　　鄭氏讀如韎韐之韎謂衣赤韍以舞也如旄人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='3294:3317'>　　　執旄以舞籥師歛籥以舞作樂名也左氏有韎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='3317:3340'>　　　韋之跗注杜氏韎赤色跗注戎服若袴而屬于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='3340:3367'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-10a' );" name="014-10a" class="pb">[014-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='3367:3390'>　　　跗與袴連此殆類赤袴亦與赤韍相似據此以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='3390:3413'>　　　作六師當如周官韎師大饗舞韎樂亦可當如</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='3413:3436'>　　　卻至衣韎韋之跗注亦可恐用周官之制為長</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='3436:3459'>　　聞事曰福禄如茨非祝人君福禄也葢人君及臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='3459:3482'>　　　下之福禄爾下文所錫是也故末章又曰福禄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='3482:3503'>　　　既同言均及之君子萬年乃祝人君之辭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='3503:3526'>總聞曰此時方㑹東都振宗周而識者已于作師之辭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='3526:3544'>多其識又先于矢其文徳王曰還歸者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='3544:3571'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-10b' );" name="014-10b" class="pb">[014-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='3571:3579'>　　裳裳者華</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='3579:3586'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='3586:3596'>裳裳者華其葉湑兮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='3596:3619'>　裳當作常常棣也其葉湑兮華凋而葉盛也芸其黄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='3619:3642'>　矣葉漸變也或黄或白葉半槁也感常棣而思賢者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='3642:3659'>　雖歴歲時漸更柯葉常欲見斯賢也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='3659:3679'>我覯之子我心寫兮我心寫兮是以有譽處兮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='3679:3686'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='3686:3713'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-11a' );" name="014-11a" class="pb">[014-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='3713:3736'>裳裳者華芸其黄矣我覯之子維其有章矣維其有章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='3736:3744'>矣是以有慶矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='3744:3751'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='3751:3774'>裳裳者華或黄或白我覯之子乗其四駱乗其四駱六</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='3774:3779'>轡沃若</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='3779:3786'>　　　四章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='3786:3809'>左之左之君子宜之右之右之君子有之維其有之是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='3809:3814'>以似之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='3814:3841'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-11b' );" name="014-11b" class="pb">[014-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='3841:3851'>　言宜在王左右也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='3851:3874'>　　聞音曰寫賞羽切慶墟羊切白僕各切左七何切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='3874:3897'>　　　今南人猶有此音吴氏以為未詳也　吴氏考</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='3897:3920'>　　　古音甚詳而采方音稍略也冝牛何切有羽軌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='3920:3930'>　　　切似飬里切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='3930:3953'>總聞曰江漢無曰予小子召公是似此當是召公之流</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='3953:3970'>其先有令名而其後能繼世象賢者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='3970:3976'>　　桑扈</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='3976:4003'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-12a' );" name="014-12a" class="pb">[014-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='4003:4010'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='4010:4020'>交交桑扈有鶯其羽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='4020:4043'>　桑扈青雀也鶯黄栗留也當是暮春毛氏鄭氏以兩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='4043:4057'>　物為一物鶯然有文章恐非</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='4057:4067'>君子樂胥受天之祜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='4067:4090'>　春深鳥飛願君子樂此景以受其福此當是人君祝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='4090:4097'>　諸侯之辭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='4097:4104'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='4104:4131'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-12b' );" name="014-12b" class="pb">[014-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='4131:4149'>交交桑扈有鶯其領君子樂胥萬邦之屏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='4149:4162'>　此當是人君譽諸侯之辭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='4162:4169'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='4169:4187'>之屏之翰百辟為憲不戢不難受福不那</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='4187:4194'>　　　四章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='4194:4212'>兕觥其觩㫖酒思柔彼交匪敖萬福來求</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='4212:4235'>　此當是人君戒諸侯之辭不可自戢而不肯為不可</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='4235:4258'>　自難而不敢為如無勉意自生退心則福不多也不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='4258:4285'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-13a' );" name="014-13a" class="pb">[014-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='4285:4308'>　戢不難如諸葛亮是也不可自敖而不勤如無逸意</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='4308:4329'>　常存勞心則福來求也彼交匪敖如陶侃是也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='4329:4352'>　　聞音曰祜侯古切翰胡干切憲虚言切難乃多切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='4352:4375'>總聞曰當是諸侯來朝而歸國餞送之際美戒兼存下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='4375:4388'>章鴛鴦似是諸侯荅君之辭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='4388:4394'>　　鴛鴦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='4394:4401'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='4401:4419'>鴛鴦于飛畢之羅之君子萬年福禄冝之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='4419:4446'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-13b' );" name="014-13b" class="pb">[014-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='4446:4469'>　畢盡也張羅者既盡則鴛鴦可以無慮也所以每章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='4469:4481'>　歸福于其君謝之辭也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='4481:4488'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='4488:4506'>鴛鴦在梁戢其左翼君子萬年宜其遐福</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='4506:4523'>　鴛鴦斂翼而休已亦可斂身而息也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='4523:4530'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='4530:4548'>乗馬在廐摧之秣之君子萬年福禄艾之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='4548:4555'>　　　四章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='4555:4582'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-14a' );" name="014-14a" class="pb">[014-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='4582:4600'>乗馬在廐秣之摧之君子萬年福禄綏之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='4600:4622'>　乗馬亦休息不慮鞭䇿已亦可休息不慮譴呵也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='4622:4645'>　　聞音曰羅鄰知切福筆力切秣莫佩切艾魚肺切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='4645:4668'>　　聞物曰鴛鴦雙棲乃能宿雄以右掩左雌以左掩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='4668:4678'>　　　右飛類皆然</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='4678:4701'>總聞曰諸侯既安心斯展力當是其君以情相留乗馬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='4701:4724'>寘之于廐而未使登塗也故諸侯即事以攄情不知的</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='4724:4740'>在何朝當似韓侯入覲出祖之時也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='4740:4767'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-14b' );" name="014-14b" class="pb">[014-14b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='4767:4773'>　　頍弁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='4773:4780'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='4780:4790'>有頍者弁實維伊何</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='4790:4813'>　當是王者親戚平時憂疑至是燕飲之際其情稍通</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='4813:4817'>　也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='4817:4840'>爾酒既㫖爾殽既嘉豈伊異人兄弟匪他蔦與女蘿施</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='4840:4845'>于松栢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='4845:4868'>　言此無他人唯我同氣下所謂具來必皆與非一人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l259' data-llen='4868:4895'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-15a' );" name="014-15a" class="pb">[014-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l260' data-llen='4895:4918'>　也下又謂甥舅必又有母黨也可謂至親可以略抒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l261' data-llen='4918:4941'>　此懐我不能自植惟恃松栢以為力哀之辭也下章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l262' data-llen='4941:4946'>　亦然</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l263' data-llen='4946:4964'>未見君子憂心弈弈既見君子庶幾悦懌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l264' data-llen='4964:4987'>　我未見不能無疑既見其疑稍釋庶幾未敢必其無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l265' data-llen='4987:4997'>　他虞也下章亦然</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l266' data-llen='4997:5004'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l267' data-llen='5004:5027'>有頍者弁實維何朝爾酒既㫖爾殽既時豈伊異人兄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l268' data-llen='5027:5054'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-15b' );" name="014-15b" class="pb">[014-15b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l269' data-llen='5054:5077'>弟具來蔦與女蘿施于松上未見君子憂心怲怲既見</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l270' data-llen='5077:5085'>君子庶幾有臧</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l271' data-llen='5085:5092'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l272' data-llen='5092:5115'>有頍者弁實維在首爾酒既㫖爾殽既阜豈伊異人兄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l273' data-llen='5115:5128'>弟甥舅如彼雨雪先集維霰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l274' data-llen='5128:5151'>　如雪先集霰漸至于大雪如讒先浸潤漸至于大禍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l275' data-llen='5151:5165'>　當是其端有緒其事将成也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l276' data-llen='5165:5183'>死喪無日無幾相見樂酒今夕君子維宴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l277' data-llen='5183:5210'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-16a' );" name="014-16a" class="pb">[014-16a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l278' data-llen='5210:5233'>　不知死當在何日見亦無幾時姑樂今夕而已訣之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l279' data-llen='5233:5238'>　辭也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l280' data-llen='5238:5261'>　　聞音曰嘉居何切他湯何切栢逋莫切弈弋灼切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l281' data-llen='5261:5284'>　　　懌弋灼切來陵之切怲被旺切臧才浪切阜房</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l282' data-llen='5284:5295'>　　　缶切舅不九切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l283' data-llen='5295:5318'>總聞曰禮貌饌具非不曲盡而我心終不能保言其人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l284' data-llen='5318:5341'>不可測也宋明帝齊髙宗猜忍之徒其于親戚骨肉之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l285' data-llen='5341:5346'>間多然</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l286' data-llen='5346:5373'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-16b' );" name="014-16b" class="pb">[014-16b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l287' data-llen='5373:5379'>　　車舝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l288' data-llen='5379:5386'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l289' data-llen='5386:5400'>間關車之舝兮思孌季女逝兮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l290' data-llen='5400:5423'>　此士大夫欲得賢女以自慰也尋詩士大夫之心甚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l291' data-llen='5423:5446'>　切當是此女之譽甚美故此士之情甚深幸而末帝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l292' data-llen='5446:5454'>　得如所願也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l293' data-llen='5454:5472'>匪飢匪渴徳音來括雖無好友式燕且喜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l294' data-llen='5472:5495'>　當是嚴車以待迎而媒妁未諧聘幣未通意不在飲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l295' data-llen='5495:5522'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-17a' );" name="014-17a" class="pb">[014-17a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l296' data-llen='5522:5545'>　食而在碩女外雖無良朋而中乃有好友殊可喜也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l297' data-llen='5545:5552'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l298' data-llen='5552:5575'>依彼平林有集維鷮辰彼碩女令徳來教式燕且譽好</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l299' data-llen='5575:5580'>爾無射</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l300' data-llen='5580:5603'>　鷮野雉也雉有謂之雉媒言安得如此人早得碩女</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l301' data-llen='5603:5623'>　來通教言此樂無有厭也因見野雉有感也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l302' data-llen='5623:5630'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l303' data-llen='5630:5653'>雖無㫖酒式飲庶幾雖無嘉殽式食庶幾雖無徳與女</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l304' data-llen='5653:5680'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-17b' );" name="014-17b" class="pb">[014-17b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l305' data-llen='5680:5686'>式歌且舞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l306' data-llen='5686:5693'>　　　四章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l307' data-llen='5693:5716'>陟彼髙岡析其柞薪析其柞薪其葉湑兮鮮我覯爾我</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l308' data-llen='5716:5721'>心寫兮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l309' data-llen='5721:5744'>　柞柞木也析良木為薪當用斧娶碩女為妻當用媒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l310' data-llen='5744:5767'>　南山伐柯之詩皆然其葉甚茂而未能析葢少肯與</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l311' data-llen='5767:5788'>　我為媒未得與碩女相見也又見茂林有感也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l312' data-llen='5788:5795'>　　　五章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l313' data-llen='5795:5822'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-18a' );" name="014-18a" class="pb">[014-18a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l314' data-llen='5822:5845'>髙山仰止景行行止四牡騑騑六轡如琴覯爾新婚以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l315' data-llen='5845:5850'>慰我心</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l316' data-llen='5850:5857'>　徃迎婚也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l317' data-llen='5857:5880'>　　聞音曰舝下瞎切逝尺列切集韻徃也吴氏舝逝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l318' data-llen='5880:5903'>　　　二韻未詳葢未考此友羽軌切鷮居妖切教居</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l319' data-llen='5903:5926'>　　　爻切射都故切薪思将切湑思叙切寫賞羽切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l320' data-llen='5926:5939'>　　　仰五剛切行户郎切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l321' data-llen='5939:5962'>總聞曰尋詩不見思君得女之意如此則似太䙝也此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l322' data-llen='5962:5989'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-18b' );" name="014-18b" class="pb">[014-18b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l323' data-llen='5989:6012'>欽慕婦賢而難得婦相見及此願有期則慰其心皆動</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l324' data-llen='6012:6022'>于己情非施于君也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l325' data-llen='6022:6028'>　　青蠅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l326' data-llen='6028:6035'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l327' data-llen='6035:6052'>營營青蠅止于樊豈弟君子無信讒言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l328' data-llen='6052:6059'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l329' data-llen='6059:6076'>營營青蠅止于棘讒人㒺極交亂四國</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l330' data-llen='6076:6083'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l331' data-llen='6083:6110'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-19a' );" name="014-19a" class="pb">[014-19a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l332' data-llen='6110:6127'>營營青蠅止于榛讒人罔極構我二人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l333' data-llen='6127:6150'>　當是為讒有端而未成也止于樊棘榛之間未至于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l334' data-llen='6150:6162'>　噆膚然不可不預慮也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l335' data-llen='6162:6173'>　　聞音曰國越逼切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l336' data-llen='6173:6196'>總聞曰二人非君臣之辭必其徒也謂君與我猶可孔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l337' data-llen='6196:6219'>氏以二人為人君與讒人不唯非君臣之禮亦語勢不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l338' data-llen='6219:6228'>順君子則指君也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l339' data-llen='6228:6236'>　　賓之初筵</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l340' data-llen='6236:6263'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-19b' );" name="014-19b" class="pb">[014-19b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l341' data-llen='6263:6270'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l342' data-llen='6270:6280'>賓之初筵左右秩秩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l343' data-llen='6280:6303'>　言延賓初入席甚整肅有次第也周制有秩酒秩膳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l344' data-llen='6303:6312'>　皆謂有常度也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l345' data-llen='6312:6335'>籩豆有楚殽核維旅酒既和㫖飲酒孔偕鐘鼔既設舉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l346' data-llen='6335:6361'>醻逸逸<span class='krp-note'>止/</span>大侯既抗弓矢斯張射夫既同獻爾發功發</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l347' data-llen='6361:6370'>彼有的以祈爾爵</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l348' data-llen='6370:6393'>　既延賓具籩豆殽核又具鐘鼔又具弓矢奏其發矢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l349' data-llen='6393:6420'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-20a' );" name="014-20a" class="pb">[014-20a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l350' data-llen='6420:6435'>　之功中的之數勝者飲不勝也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l351' data-llen='6435:6442'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l352' data-llen='6442:6468'>籥舞笙鼔樂既和奏烝衎烈祖<span class='krp-note'>止/</span>以洽百禮百禮既至</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l353' data-llen='6468:6494'><span class='krp-note'>止/</span>有壬有林錫爾純嘏子孫其湛其湛曰樂各奏爾能</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l354' data-llen='6494:6517'>　既起射具樂舞笙鼔而獻先祖其禮至百又盛大于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l355' data-llen='6517:6540'>　初嘏傳尸辭以飲福也飲福既畢又各奏其閑射之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l356' data-llen='6540:6548'>　能以相校也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l357' data-llen='6548:6566'>賓載手仇室人入又酌彼康爵以奏爾時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l358' data-llen='6566:6593'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-20b' );" name="014-20b" class="pb">[014-20b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l359' data-llen='6593:6616'>　既奏能又起射以手為匹言分耦也酌爵以飲不勝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l360' data-llen='6616:6639'>　各奏其時言不踰所當酌之時告之于尸也初筵大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l361' data-llen='6639:6662'>　率兩射賓飲酒既遍之後一也尸受饗既畢之後一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l362' data-llen='6662:6675'>　也其率禮如此所謂秩也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l363' data-llen='6675:6682'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l364' data-llen='6682:6696'>賓之初筵<span class='krp-note'>止/</span>温温其恭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l365' data-llen='6696:6719'>　再舉初筵言勞賓饗神皆如禮上二章是也過此則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l366' data-llen='6719:6733'>　酒皆酣禮皆廢下二章是也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l367' data-llen='6733:6760'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-21a' );" name="014-21a" class="pb">[014-21a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l368' data-llen='6760:6783'>其未醉止威儀反反曰既醉止威儀幡幡舍其坐遷屢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l369' data-llen='6783:6806'>舞僊僊其未醉止威儀抑抑曰既醉止威儀怭怭是曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l370' data-llen='6806:6814'>既醉不知其秩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l371' data-llen='6814:6824'>　向之秩今皆忘也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l372' data-llen='6824:6831'>　　　四章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l373' data-llen='6831:6857'>賓既醉止載號載呶亂我籩豆<span class='krp-note'>止/</span>屢舞僛僛是曰既醉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l374' data-llen='6857:6883'>不知其郵<span class='krp-note'>止/</span>側弁之俄屢舞傞傞既醉而出並受其福</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l375' data-llen='6883:6901'>醉而不出是謂伐徳飲酒孔嘉維其令儀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l376' data-llen='6901:6928'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-21b' );" name="014-21b" class="pb">[014-21b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l377' data-llen='6928:6951'>　數其状也有醉而出者則受福之人言不至蹈害也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l378' data-llen='6951:6974'>　有醉而不出者則伐徳之人必至喪善也亦有飲而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l379' data-llen='6974:6997'>　甚嘉不失其令儀葢亦有賢者不皆小人也所以下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l380' data-llen='6997:7010'>　章凡此飲酒或醉或否也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l381' data-llen='7010:7017'>　　　五章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l382' data-llen='7017:7040'>凡此飲酒或醉或否既立之監或佐之史彼醉不臧不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l383' data-llen='7040:7045'>醉反恥</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l384' data-llen='7045:7068'>　監史所以糾飲酒過度者也至醉者固為不善當糾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l385' data-llen='7068:7095'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-22a' );" name="014-22a" class="pb">[014-22a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l386' data-llen='7095:7118'>　之也反以不醉為恥監史不以糾醉為職乃以縱醉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l387' data-llen='7118:7132'>　為能也五代閩之王氏若此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l388' data-llen='7132:7142'>式勿從謂無俾大怠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l389' data-llen='7142:7165'>　大率醉者諱人勸止而醒者不忍坐視也式勿從謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l390' data-llen='7165:7188'>　言勿從而告之也無俾大怠但可扶持使不至于太</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l391' data-llen='7188:7194'>　顛仆也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l392' data-llen='7194:7217'>匪言勿言匪由勿語由醉之言俾出童羖三爵不識矧</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l393' data-llen='7217:7222'>敢多又</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l394' data-llen='7222:7249'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-22b' );" name="014-22b" class="pb">[014-22b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l395' data-llen='7249:7272'>　醒者相與為戒非所當言者勿言非所當從者勿語</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l396' data-llen='7272:7295'>　謂勸止也若可從而言莫若勸其出童持車之僕也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l397' data-llen='7295:7318'>　羖駕車之羊也言乗車而去也然三爵之後則不識</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l398' data-llen='7318:7341'>　義理不識親朋童羖之言已過况敢多言多言則醉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l399' data-llen='7341:7350'>　者興怒見犯也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l400' data-llen='7350:7373'>　　聞音曰兩舉賓之初筵即大章首題也初賓之初</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l401' data-llen='7373:7396'>　　　筵下衍一章次賓之初筵下衍二章兩大章竝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l402' data-llen='7396:7419'>　　　一句單入其餘不然㫖旁紐作陟叶逸設書實</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l403' data-llen='7419:7446'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-23a' );" name="014-23a" class="pb">[014-23a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l404' data-llen='7446:7469'>　　　切抗居郎切的丁樂切湛持林切仇又相叶又</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l405' data-llen='7469:7492'>　　　旁紐作尤康旁紐入聲作恪叶爵爾旁紐平聲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l406' data-llen='7492:7515'>　　　作而叶時此隨句取叶也大率不叶者委曲取</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l407' data-llen='7515:7538'>　　　叶亦無有不叶者反芬邅切郵旁紐作宥叶豆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l408' data-llen='7538:7561'>　　　醉者阻人勸止之聲若又今西北人猶有此聲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l409' data-llen='7561:7584'>　　　大率厭却煩聒雖不醉亦多稱又出尺律切福</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l410' data-llen='7584:7607'>　　　筆力切嘉居何切儀牛何切否補美切史炎士</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l411' data-llen='7607:7625'>　　　切怠飬里切羖公土切又夷益切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l412' data-llen='7625:7652'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-23b' );" name="014-23b" class="pb">[014-23b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l413' data-llen='7652:7675'>　　聞事曰手左右出耦亦左右出故耦從手也舊改</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l414' data-llen='7675:7685'>　　　手作耦不必</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l415' data-llen='7685:7708'>　　聞用曰古者車乗首以馬次以牛次以羊輕小之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l416' data-llen='7708:7723'>　　　車羊駕之所謂灑鹽者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l417' data-llen='7723:7746'>　　聞人曰周制酒正不唯以式法授酒材所謂酌數</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l418' data-llen='7746:7769'>　　　器量皆掌其政令王之燕飲共其訃酒正奉之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l419' data-llen='7769:7792'>　　　訃謂獻酧多少監或謂此史即府史之屬左氏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l420' data-llen='7792:7805'>　　　屠蒯請佐使尊恐是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l421' data-llen='7805:7832'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '014-24a' );" name="014-24a" class="pb">[014-24a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l422' data-llen='7832:7855'>總聞曰此同在席醒者談醉者之状當怒而不怒當責</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l423' data-llen='7855:7878'>而不責乃更委曲保䕶醒者必慈祥長厚之人憚凶徳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l424' data-llen='7878:7895'>憐狂夫而又逺害者也令儀葢斯人耶</span><br/>
